TopicTitle: Could someone please tell me what causes this crash?

Articles.Content: You're running out of memory because you're using the 32bit version.

3 minutes ago, Harry Rhodan said:

You're running out of memory because you're using the 32bit version.

So steam places the 32 bit launcher as an icon by default? Oh joy... 

I excluded the possibility, thinking that I just installed a steam version on a 64 bit system... Thanks for the info, but now I feel kinda dumb...
